    "gripper_formula": "aperture=q_left-q_right; deterministic two-cluster median centers; theta_closed=closed+gap/3; theta_open=open-gap/3; state flip or hysteresis-band occupancy plus two-tick cooldown vetoes skip",
    "decision_formula": "skip iff current and previous finite-difference samples are within all frozen motion thresholds and neither observed nor issued gripper commands transition; otherwise infer"
